              "id": "we_math_7_T10_1",
              "prompt": "Evaluate $\\int x e^x\\,dx$ by parts.",
              "steps": [
                "Let $u = x$, $dv = e^x\\,dx$. Then $du = dx$, $v = e^x$.",
                "$\\int u\\,dv = uv - \\int v\\,du = xe^x - \\int e^x\\,dx$.",
                "So $\\int xe^x\\,dx = xe^x - e^x + C = e^x(x-1) + C$."
              ],
              "finalAnswer": "$e^x(x - 1) + C$.",
              "_source": "Authored from NCERT/ISC pattern"
