              "id": "we_math_10_T14_1",
              "prompt": "Find the area of the parallelogram with adjacent sides $\\vec a = \\hat i + \\hat j$ and $\\vec b = \\hat j + \\hat k$.",
              "steps": [
                "$\\vec a\\times\\vec b = \\det\\begin{pmatrix} \\hat i & \\hat j & \\hat k \\\\ 1 & 1 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 1 & 1\\end{pmatrix} = (1-0)\\hat i - (1-0)\\hat j + (1-0)\\hat k = \\hat i - \\hat j + \\hat k$.",
                "Area $= |\\vec a\\times\\vec b| = \\sqrt{1+1+1} = \\sqrt 3$."
              ],
              "finalAnswer": "Area $= \\sqrt 3$ sq. units.",
